# MFE Development

Guide for teams building new Micro-Frontends on the DXP platform.

## Scaffold a New MFE

```bash
pnpm --filter @dxp/create-mfe run scaffold my-mfe
```

This generates the complete MFE skeleton with all required config files.

## Required Patterns

### Entry Point

```typescript
// src/index.ts — single line only
import('./bootstrap');
```

### Bootstrap

```typescript
// src/bootstrap.tsx
import('./App');
```

### Mount (required default export)

```typescript
// src/mount.tsx
const mount: MFEMountFn = (container, props) => {
  container.classList.toggle('dark', props.theme.mode === 'dark');
  const root = createRoot(container);
  root.render(<App {...props} />);
  return { unmount: () => { root.unmount(); container.classList.remove('dark'); } };
};
export default mount;
```

